---
title: BBQ Pulled Pork & Brioche Subs with Crunchy Slaw & Potato Wedges
description: This loaded sub has incredible flavour to match its incredible size. Coated in a saucy mixture of pulled pork and BBQ sauce, you'll
never have subs any other way again!
